## Project sources of truth

- `src/sass/_variables.scss` — client tokens (colors, typography, breakpoints)
- `src/sass/main.scss` — partial import order
- `www/templates/` — HTML templates (pages, blocks, header, footer)
- `src/js/main.js` — JS entry point

## Common commands

```bash
cd src && pnpm install
cd src && pnpm start:dev   # Gulp watch (dev)
cd src && pnpm start       # production build
```

